section_summary: The text appears to be a list of individuals taking an oath of loyalty to their country, prince, constitution, and laws. The names mentioned are Dr. Janan Mohsen Ramadan, Dr. Hassan Abdullah Jawhar, Hamad Adel Al-Obaid, and Hamad Abdulrahman Al-Alyan. The text also mentions the General Secretariat of the Council of Ministers and the management of sessions. The date mentioned is June 20, 2023, and the page number is 61.
